VE does not display the panel being designed correctly.

I believe this is caused by the same problem in bug 105402.
VE uses a remote VM to render the live Swing components and does screen scraping
back to the main IDE to show the actual WYSIWYG in the editor. Calls are made to
the remote VM via TCP/IP socket protocols.

Since your firewall is interferring with this process, you are experiencing
these types of problems.

*** This bug has been marked as a duplicate of 105402 ***
